room_title: Escape room "The Haunting of Camp Rutledge" by Escape Plan Georgia in Atlanta
room_address: 3735 Harrison Road SW, Suite 600, Loganville, GA 30052
room_description: Rumor has it that Camp Rutledge is haunted! A ghostly young boy named Ethan with a red ball appears running in the woods and vanishes. Do you have what it takes to escape and solve the mystery of what happened to Ethan and his red ball?
